'''羅塞塔號'''（{{lang|en|Rosetta}}）是[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]]組織的[[機器人|機器人]][[空间探测器|空间探测器]]計劃，研究[[67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希门克彗星|67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希门克彗星]]。<ref name="NASA-20140630">{{cite web |last=Agle |first=DC |last2=Brown |first2=Dwayne |last3=Bauer |first3=Markus |title=Rosetta's Comet Target 'Releases' Plentiful Water |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-212 |date=30 June 2014 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=30 June 2014 |archive-date=2022-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220325072731/https://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-212 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT-20140805">{{cite news |last=Chang |first=Kenneth |title=Rosetta Spacecraft Set for Unprecedented Close Study of a Comet |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/06/science/space/rosetta-spacecraft-set-for-unprecedented-close-study-of-a-comet.html |date=5 August 2014 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=5 August 2014 |archive-date=2014-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807091744/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/06/science/space/rosetta-spacecraft-set-for-unprecedented-close-study-of-a-comet.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2004年3月2日在[[蓋亞那太空中心|蓋亞那太空中心]]發射，10年8個多月後進入彗星軌道，隨後其所攜帶的[[菲萊登陸器|菲萊登陸器]]則於2014年11月12日在彗星上著陸。在2014年8月6日它接近到彗星約{{convert|100|km|abbr=on}}的距離，並降低其相對速度為{{convert|1|m/s|abbr=on}}，從而成為意圖會合彗星而進入其軌道的第一個航天器。<ref>{{cite news |last=Kramer |first=Miriam |url=http://www.space.com/26754-rosetta-comet-spacecraft-5-amazing-facts.html?cmpid=514630_20140807_29286356 |title=5 Amazing Facts about Europe's Comet-Chasing Rosetta Probe |work=Space.com |date=August 6, 2014 |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archive-date=2021-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409011000/https://www.space.com/26754-rosetta-comet-spacecraft-5-amazing-facts.html?cmpid=514630_20140807_29286356 |dead-url=no }}</ref>經過進一步的機動，計劃是接近到{{convert|30|km|abbr=on}}後和大約6週後進入軌道。<ref name="Fischer2014-08-06">{{cite web|url=http://www.planetary.org/blogs/guest-blogs/2014/0806-fischer-rendezvous-with-a-crazy-world.html |title=Rendezvous with a crazy world |publisher=[[The_Planetary_Society|The Planetary Society]] |first=D. |last=Fischer |date=6 August 2014 |accessdate=6 August 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140806210446/http://www.planetary.org/blogs/guest-blogs/2014/0806-fischer-rendezvous-with-a-crazy-world.html |archivedate=2014-08-06|deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Bauer2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Rosetta_arrives_at_comet_destination |title=Rosetta Arrives at Comet Destination |publisher=[[European_Space_Agency|European Space Agency]] |first=M. |last=Bauer |date=6 August 2014 |accessdate=6 August 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140806111419/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Rosetta_arrives_at_comet_destination |archivedate=2014-08-06|deadurl=no }}</ref>它是[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]]{{link-fr|地平線2000|Horizon 2000}}基礎任務的一部分，和它是被設計成既軌道環繞彗星又登陸彗星的第一個任務。<ref name="NASA-201401017">{{cite web |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-015 |title=Rosetta: To Chase a Comet |publisher=NASA |first1=D. C. |last1=Agle |first2=Jia-Rui |last2=Cook |first3=Dwayne |last3=Brown |first4=Markus |last4=Bauer |date=17 January 2014 |accessdate=18 January 2014 |archive-date=2016-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113181033/http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

羅塞塔號于2004年3月2日[[格林威治時間|格林威治時間]]07:17由[[亞利安五號運載火箭|亞利安五號運載火箭]]發射，在2014年8月6日到達彗星。<ref name="OCM">{{cite web |url=http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2014/05/07/thruster-burn-kicks-off-crucial-series-of-manoeuvres// |title=Thruster burn kicks off crucial series of manoeuvres |publisher=European Space Agency |first=Daniel |last=Scuka |date=7 May 2014 |accessdate=21 May 2014 |archive-date=2014-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140521220918/http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2014/05/07/thruster-burn-kicks-off-crucial-series-of-manoeuvres/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>羅塞塔號由兩個主要部件組成：'''羅塞塔探測器'''，其中帶有12個儀器，及'''[[菲萊登陸器|菲萊登陸器]]'''，其中帶有另外的9個儀器。<ref name="ESA">{{cite web|url=http://www.esa.int/esaMI/Rosetta/SEMYMF374OD_0.html |title=Rosetta at a glance |publisher=European Space Agency |accessdate=4 October 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514003109/http://www.esa.int/esaMI/Rosetta/SEMYMF374OD_0.html |archivedate=2011-05-14|deadurl=yes }}</ref>羅塞塔號的任務將軌道環繞[[67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希门克彗星|67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希门克彗星]]17個月，並且被設計來完成對於彗星有史以來嘗試的最詳細的一個研究。任務是被從在德國[[達姆施塔特|達姆施塔特]]的[[歐洲太空運營中心|歐洲太空運營中心]]（ESOC）控制。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/01/20/world/europe/rosetta-comet-probe/index.html |title=Comet-chasing probe wakes up, calls home |work=CNN |first1=Michael |last1=Pearson |first2=Matt |last2=Smith |date=21 January 2014 |accessdate=21 January 2014 |archive-date=2021-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409011034/https://edition.cnn.com/2014/01/20/world/europe/rosetta-comet-probe/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

探測器以[[羅塞塔石碑|羅塞塔石碑]]為命名，希望此任務能幫助解開行星形成前的[[太陽系|太陽系]]的謎。而登陸器以[[尼羅河|尼羅河]]中小島的名字''菲萊''命名，有一塊方尖碑在那裡被發現且協助解讀羅塞塔石碑。對[[羅塞塔石碑|羅塞塔石碑]]和方尖碑的[[象形文字|象形文字]]的比較，催化埃及的書寫系統的解密。同樣，人們希望這些飛船將導致更好的理解彗星和早期[[太陽系|太陽系]]。<ref name="space20140115">{{cite news |url=http://www.space.com/24292-rosetta-spacecraft.html |title=Rosetta Spacecraft: To Catch a Comet |work=Space.com |first=Tim |last=Sharp |date=15 January 2014 |accessdate=25 January 2014 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417225056/https://www.space.com/24292-rosetta-spacecraft.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="esaint20040205">{{cite news |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Unlocking_the_secrets_of_the_universe_Rosetta_lander_named_Philae |title=Unlocking the secrets of the universe: Rosetta lander named Philae |publisher=European Space Agency |date=5 February 2004 |accessdate=25 January 2014 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616202451/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Unlocking_the_secrets_of_the_universe_Rosetta_lander_named_Philae |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在它飛向彗星的途中，飛船已經完成2[[小行星|小行星]]的飛掠任務。<ref>{{cite journal |title=The Rosetta Mission: Flying Towards the Origin of the Solar System |journal=Space Science Reviews |first1=Karl-Heinz |last1=Glassmeier |first2=Hermann |last2=Boehnhardt |first3=Detlef |last3=Koschny |first4=Ekkehard |last4=Kührt |first5=Ingo |last5=Richter |volume=128 |issue=1–4 |pages=1–21 |date=February 2007 |doi=10.1007/s11214-006-9140-8 |bibcode=2007SSRv..128....1G}}</ref>在2007年，罗塞塔号还进行了火星[[重力助推|重力助推变轨]]（飞越）。<ref name="Mars fly-by">{{cite news|url=http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Rosetta/SEMUDT70LYE_0.html |title=Beautiful new images from Rosetta's approach to Mars: OSIRIS Update |publisher=European Space Agency |first1=Uwe |last1=Keller |first2=Gerhard |last2=Schwehm |date=25 February 2007 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070227132949/http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/Rosetta/SEMUDT70LYE_0.html |archivedate=2007-02-27|deadurl=yes }}</ref>

罗塞塔号的[[菲莱登陆器|菲莱登陆器]]于2014年11月12日在彗星上登陆，就是[[67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希门克彗星|67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希门克彗星]]，成为有史以来第一个在彗星上的成功受控登陆的探测器。<ref name="NASA-20141112-DCA">{{cite web |last=Agle |first=DC |last2=Webster |first2=Guy |last3=Brown |first3=Dwayne |last4=Bauer |first4=Markus |title=Rosetta's 'Philae' Makes Historic First Landing on a Comet |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-394 |date=12 November 2014 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=13 November 2014 |archive-date=2019-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190124141327/https://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-394 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT-20141112-KC">{{cite news |last=Chang |first=Kenneth |title=European Space Agency’s Spacecraft Lands on Comet’s Surface |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/13/science/space/european-space-agencys-spacecraft-lands-on-comets-surface.html |date=12 November 2014 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=12 November 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112192922/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/13/science/space/european-space-agencys-spacecraft-lands-on-comets-surface.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://news.sky.com/story/1371730/rosetta-comet-probe-beams-back-pictures|title = Rosetta: Comet Probe Beams Back Pictures|date = 12 November 2012|accessdate = 12 November 2012|website = Rosetta: Comet Probe Beams Back Pictures|publisher = SkyNews|archive-date = 2015-10-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151009150312/http://news.sky.com/story/1371730/rosetta-comet-probe-beams-back-pictures|dead-url = no}}</ref>天体物理学家伊丽莎白·皮尔逊说，虽然菲莱登陆器的未来是不确定的，但是轨道器罗塞塔号是任务的主力，并且它的工作将继续。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-30066774|title = Philae: Its done what it went there to do|date = 15 November 2014|accessdate = 15 November 2014|website = Philae: Its done what it went there to do|publisher = BBCNews|archive-date = 2015-09-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925192526/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-30066774|dead-url = no}}</ref>

