* 3月16日 - 觀察到[[P/2010_A2|P/2010 A2]]小行星塵埃尾巴。連同[[哈勃空间望远镜|哈勃空间望远镜]]的觀察就可以確認[[P/2010_A2|P/2010 A2]]不是一顆彗星，而是一顆小行星，並且該塵埃尾巴很可能是由從一個較小的小行星的撞擊产生的塵埃而形成。<ref>{{cite journal |title=A collision in 2009 as the origin of the debris trail of asteroid P/2010 A2 |journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]] |first1=Colin |last1=Snodgrass |first2=Cecilia |last2=Tubiana |first3=Jean-Baptiste |last3=Vincent |first4=Holger |last4=Sierks |first5=Stubbe |last5=Hviid |first6=Richard |last6=Moissl |first7=Hermann |last7=Boehnhardt |first8=Cesare |last8=Barbieri |first9=Detlef |last9=Koschny |first10=Philippe |last10=Lamy |first11=Hans |last11=Rickman |first12=Rafael |last12=Rodrigo |first13=Benoît |last13=Carry |first14=Stephen C. |last14=Lowry |first15=Ryan J. M. |last15=Laird |first16=Paul R. |last16=Weissman |first17=Alan |last17=Fitzsimmons |first18=Simone |last18=Marchi |author19=OSIRIS team |display-authors=5 |volume=467 |issue=7317 |pages=814–816 |date=October 2010 |doi=10.1038/nature09453 |bibcode=2010Natur.467..814S |pmid=20944742 |arxiv=1010.2883}}</ref>
* 7月10日 - 飛過並拍攝了小行星[[司琴星|司琴星]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.space.com/8740-mysterious-asteroid-unmasked-space-probe-flyby.html |title=Mysterious Asteroid Unmasked By Space Probe Flyby |work=Space.com |first=Denise |last=Chow |date=10 July 2010 |accessdate=10 July 2010 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309161549/https://www.space.com/8740-mysterious-asteroid-unmasked-space-probe-flyby.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

;2011年
* 6月8日 - 該航天器轉移到自旋穩定方式，除了飛船電腦和休眠加熱器，所有電子設備被關閉。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Rosetta_comet_probe_enters_hibernation_in_deep_space |title=Rosetta comet probe enters hibernation in deep space |publisher=European Space Agency |date=8 June 2011 |accessdate=8 June 2011 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616014429/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Rosetta_comet_probe_enters_hibernation_in_deep_space |dead-url=no }}</ref>

;2014年
* 1月20日 - 在10:00 UTC 歐洲航天局接收到羅塞塔號飛船的電腦從[[休眠_(電腦)|休眠]]甦醒出來的信號。在18:18 UTC羅塞塔通過NASA的戈德斯通地面站恢復ESOC通信。<ref name="science20140120">{{cite news |url=http://news.sciencemag.org/europe/2014/01/rosetta-awakes-and-prepares-chase-comet |title=Rosetta Awakes and Prepares to Chase Comet |work=[[Science_(journal)|Science]] |first=Daniel |last=Clery |date=20 January 2014 |accessdate=22 January 2014 |archive-date=2014-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201155027/http://news.sciencemag.org/europe/2014/01/rosetta-awakes-and-prepares-chase-comet |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="rosettaWakeUp">{{cite news |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/ESA_s_sleeping_beauty_wakes_up_from_deep_space_hibernation |title=ESA's 'sleeping beauty' wakes up from deep space hibernation |publisher=European Space Agency |date=20 January 2014 |accessdate=20 January 2014 |archive-date=2019-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622020506/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/ESA_s_sleeping_beauty_wakes_up_from_deep_space_hibernation |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 5月至7月 - 羅塞塔號運行至距目標彗星約200萬公里處，向地球傳回了彗星的首批圖像。
* 8月6日 - 抵達彗星附近{{convert|100|km|abbr=on}}，飛船行駛的速度是{{convert|1|m/s|abbr=on}}。<ref name="bigburns02">{{cite web |url=http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2014/06/03/the-big-burns-part-2/ |title=The Big Burns – Part 2 |publisher=European Space Agency |first=Daniel |last=Scuka |date=3 June 2014 |accessdate=9 June 2014 |archive-date=2014-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140616055309/http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2014/06/03/the-big-burns-part-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/esaoperations/status/496951358143336449 |title=Thruster burn complete |publisher=Twitter.com |author=ESA Operations |date=6 August 2014 |accessdate=6 August 2014 |archive-date=2019-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120113126/https://twitter.com/esaoperations/status/496951358143336449 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="mirror20140806">{{cite news |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/technology-science/science/rosetta-probe-live-updates-spacecraft-3996770 |title=Rosetta probe: Recap updates after spacecraft successfully reached deep space comet orbit |work=[[Daily_Mirror|Daily Mirror]] |first=Sam |last=Rkaina |date=6 August 2014 |accessdate=6 August 2014}}</ref>開始對彗星表面進行為期兩個月的繪圖，探測其引力、質量、形狀和大氣等。彗星測繪和鑑定一個穩定的軌道，以確定[[菲萊登陸器|菲萊]]可行的著陸位置。<ref name="bbc20140814">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-28741244 |title=Rosetta: Comet probe gets down to work |work=BBC News |first=Jonathan |last=Amos |date=14 August 2014 |accessdate=15 August 2014 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031323/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-28741244 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

* 9月 - 羅塞塔進入{{convert|30|km|abbr=on}}的高度的全彗星測圖軌道。
* 11月12日 - 探测器“[[菲萊登陸器|菲萊登陸器]]”於15:35 UTC的時候成功於67P/G-C彗星表面著陸。這是人類歷史上第一次讓航天器在彗星上登陸，經過0:28:20的信號傳遞時間，於16:03獲得證實<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Three_touchdowns_for_Rosetta_s_lander |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-12-12 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225230212/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Three_touchdowns_for_Rosetta_s_lander%20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 11月15日 - 探测器“[[菲萊登陸器|菲萊登陸器]]”因為電力不足，利用僅存的電力進入休眠狀態，休眠前ESA團隊調整菲萊的太陽能板角度，雖然菲萊降落地點位於坑洞陰影中導致效果不盡理想，但仍希望67P/G-C彗星接近太陽時，能夠有機會接收到足夠的太陽能產生電力，再次喚醒菲萊進一步研究彗星。而羅賽塔對67P/G-C彗星的繞行觀測任務仍持續進行中。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Pioneering_Philae_completes_main_mission_before_hibernation |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-11-21 |archive-date=2014-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141118204308/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Pioneering_Philae_completes_main_mission_before_hibernation |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 12月10日 - ROSINA質譜儀顯示彗星67P上[[重水|重水]]對水的比率是地球上的三倍以上。這個比率被視爲一種獨特的標記，該發現意味著地球上的水不太可能來源於像67P這樣的彗星。<ref name="NASA-20141210-DCA">{{cite web |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-423 |title=Rosetta Instrument Reignites Debate on Earth's Oceans |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |first1=D. C. |last1=Agle |first2=Markus |last2=Bauer |date=10 December 2014 |accessdate=10 December 2014 |archive-date=2014-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211044911/http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-423 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT-20141210-KC">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/11/science/rosetta-mission-data-rules-out-comets-as-a-source-for-earths-water.html |title=Comet Data Clears Up Debate on Earth's Water |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |first=Kenneth |last=Chang |date=10 December 2014 |accessdate=10 December 2014 |archive-date=2018-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617060514/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/11/science/rosetta-mission-data-rules-out-comets-as-a-source-for-earths-water.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC-20141211">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-30414519 |title=Rosetta results: Comets 'did not bring water to Earth' |work=BBC News |first=Rebecca |last=Morelle |date=10 December 2014 |accessdate=11 December 2014 |archive-date=2018-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180425130712/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-30414519 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
;2015年
* 2015年4月14日 - 科學家指出67P的彗核沒有自身的磁場。<ref name="esa20150414">{{cite news |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Rosetta_and_Philae_find_comet_not_magnetised |title=Rosetta and Philae Find Comet Not Magnetised |publisher=European Space Agency |first=Markus |last=Bauer |date=14 April 2015 |accessdate=14 April 2015 |archive-date=2017-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171207054405/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Rosetta_and_Philae_find_comet_not_magnetised |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*2015年7月，探測船於繞行「[[楚留莫夫－格拉希門克彗星|楚留莫夫－格拉希門克彗星]]（67P/Churyumov- Gerasimenko）」時，拍攝到彗星上，一處被命名為「阿斯旺（Aswan）」的懸崖山壁處噴發大量煙塵，推論可能發生「山崩」現象。研究單位預計將此研究結果，刊登於「自然天文學」（NatureAstronomy）期刊上<ref>{{cite news|title=羅賽塔首次拍到 彗星懸崖崩塌畫面|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/ait/201703220462-1.aspx|publisher=中央通訊社|date=2017-03-21|author=|accessdate=2017-03-22|archive-date=2017-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170502100127/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/ait/201703220462-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* 2014年11月至2015年12月 - 羅塞塔護送圍繞太陽的彗星。

